title: Moderator Compensation
body:
The Head Moderators and the Moderators are not compensated from team rewards as they are not a part of the team, but rather are from the DAO Community and work on behalf of the DAO Community. This proposal is in regards to moderator compensation from the DAO wallet:

Should the mod team be compensated?

If we vote yes, there will be a follow up vote on the amount of compensation.
